00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:39,219
Jiang Xiaoning, when did you start reporting directly to Director Gu about projects?

523
00:35:39,219 --> 00:35:41,440
I... I didn't.

524
00:35:41,440 --> 00:35:43,139
This photography exhibition project.

525
00:35:43,139 --> 00:35:46,600
Didn't you go over my head and report it to Director Gu directly?

526
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:49,839
I'm sorry, Sister Manlin. I didn't think it through.

527
00:35:49,839 --> 00:35:52,059
Think more before you act next time.

528
00:35:52,059 --> 00:35:53,760
Let's go.

529
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:06,759
Sister Wenwen, sorry you had to wait.

530
00:36:06,759 --> 00:36:08,640
No problem.

531
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:14,660
This is the Vice President and Design Director, Su Manlin.

532
00:36:14,660 --> 00:36:18,779
Sister Manlin, this is my friend. A photographer, Chen Wenwen.

533
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:25,040
Turning this space into an exhibition hall is a nice idea.

534
