The view is unobstructed and the space is large enough.

535
00:36:27,559 --> 00:36:29,940
More importantly, the price is reasonable.

536
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:34,299
However, it might be a little difficult to construct.

537
00:36:34,299 --> 00:36:36,739
Transportation of materials will be a problem, too.

538
00:36:36,739 --> 00:36:40,099
And we're not sure if it'll take a long time to receive approval.

539
00:36:40,099 --> 00:36:42,119
That's not a problem. I've got time.

540
00:36:42,119 --> 00:36:47,850
- I'm just thinking... 
 - It'll be impossible for the entire space to be used for the exhibition.

541
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:50,780
That's fine. Half will be enough.

542
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:52,940
Even half will be too much.

543
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:58,460
My advice is to make a third into indoor space

544
00:36:58,460 --> 00:37:01,760
and make the rest into a resting area.

545
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:05,880
Then integrate some landscaping into the exhibition area.

546
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:07,919
I don't think that's a good idea.

547
00:37:07,919 --> 00:37:10,420
- Landscaping... 
 - The addition of a garden design

548
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:12,899
